<h2>
    Main Method
</h2>
<p>
    Every Java program has a main method: without it, the program won't run. 
    This must be inside a class (all methods must). The class name should also 
    match the filename. 
</p>
<pre><code class="lang-java">// Example.java
public class Example {
    // main method 
    public static void main(String[] args){
        System.out.println("Example");
        // Example
    }
}</code></pre>

